</P>
<P>
 Howard Shangraw: Fred / Gentleman on the Street 
</P>
<P>
 John Ellington: Bob Cratchit 
</P>
<P>
 Sharon Omi: Mrs. Cratchit / Rich Woman 
</P>
<P>
 Art Koustik: Mr. Fezziwig / Joe 
</P>
<P>
