<HEADLINE>
<P>
'CHRISTMASTIME' AT CARPENTER CENTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The South Coast Chorale, a Los Angeles County-based gay and lesbian chorus, 
will give two performances of its 1994 "Christmastime" concert at the Richard 
and Karen Carpenter Performing Arts Center at Cal State Long Beach. 
</P>
