</P>
<P>
 5120 Bonita Canyon Road, Irvine 
</P>
<P>
 (714) 730-6337.  
</P>
<P>
 * Sunday, Dec. 11, at 11 a.m. 
</P>
<P>
 The Life Church 
</P>
<P>
 27129 Calle Arroyo, San Juan Capistrano 
</P>
<P>
 (714) 248-7729 
</P>
<P>
 * Dec. 19 (time unavailable) 
</P>
<P>
