</P>
<P>
 (714) 631-2880 
</P>
<P>
 * Jan. 22, at 6 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Eastside Christian Church 
</P>
<P>
 2505 E. Yorba Linda Blvd., Fullerton 
</P>
