<P>
 In another game of the Irvine tournament: 
</P>
<P>
 Laguna Hills 1, Irvine 0 -- Kevin McConaughy's goal 10 minutes into the second 
half lifted Laguna Hills (3-2-0) in the fifth-place semifinal game. 
