Rachel Beardslee and Lily Maniaci posted a shutout for the Eagles (2-1). 
</P>
<P>
 Costa Mesa 9, Rancho Alamitos 0 -- Jessica Schroeder scored five goals to lead 
Costa Mesa (3-1). Teammates Mandy Simones, Gegi Van de Walker, Shirley Blassman 
and Jamie Benson each added one. 
</P>
