<BYLINE>
<P>
By DAVE DESMOND 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Christian Fauria of the University of Colorado was named an Associated Press 
third-team All-American on Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Fauria is a senior tight end who graduated from Crespi High in 1990. 
</P>
<P>
 Colorado will play Notre Dame in the Fiesta Bowl on Jan. 2. Girls' Softball 
</P>
<P>
