0-2) did not have a shot on goal. 
</P>
<P>
 Hart 1, Palmdale 1 -- Vanessa Ferra scored early in the second half for Hart, 
which held on for a nonleague tie. BOYS' SOCCER 
</P>
<P>
 Chatsworth 3, Birmingham 3 -- Edwin Esperanza of Birmingham scored his second 
goal of the Northwest Valley Conference match with only minutes to play to 
forge a tie at Birmingham. 
</P>
