</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Police are investigating the shooting death of a 24-year-old man found Tuesday 
in an apartment in the 1000 block of South Philadelphia Street. 
</P>
<P>
 Isabel D. Martinez of Anaheim was shot once in the upper torso and died at the 
scene at 9:30 p.m., according to Sgt. Steve Rodig, of the homicide detail. 
</P>
<P>
 Investigators are looking into the possibility that Martinez might have been 
the victim of a robbery attempt, Rodig said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
