 * Per-capita income: $19,890 (1990) 
</P>
<P>
 * Median household income: $45,922 (1990) 
</P>
<P>
 County Budget Trend (in billions) '94-95: $3.6 Sources: Orange County, U.S. 
Census, California Department of Finance, Times reports  
