<HEADLINE>
<P>
OBITUARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Bertoia, Daniel Joseph, 30, of Westlake Village, self-employed computer 
analyst. Pierce Brothers Valley Oaks, Westlake Village. 
</P>
<P>
 Fretwell, Harry Alfred, 76, of Ojai, rancher. Ted Mayr Funeral Home, Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Scott, Bessie M., 102, of Ojai, homemaker. Ted Mayr Funeral Home, Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura County obituaries are published free of charge as a public service to 
readers. Obituaries are based on information provided by mortuaries. 
</P>
